  • Classes in rocks.xmpp.extensions.data.model used by rocks.xmpp.extensions.data 
    Class Description
    DataForm
    The implementation of the <x/> element in the jabber:x:data namespace, which represents data forms.
  • Classes in rocks.xmpp.extensions.data.model used by rocks.xmpp.extensions.data.model 
    Class Description
    DataForm
    The implementation of the <x/> element in the jabber:x:data namespace, which represents data forms.
    DataForm.Builder
    An abstract builder to build simple data forms.
    DataForm.Field
    A data form field.
    DataForm.Field.Builder
    A builder class to build a data form field.
    DataForm.Field.Type
    Defines field types.
    DataForm.Item
    An item which can be understood as a table row.
    DataForm.Option
    Defines an option in a field of type DataForm.Field.Type.LIST_SINGLE or DataForm.Field.Type.LIST_MULTI.
    DataForm.Type
    The form type.
